# RF Propagation Modeling

## Overview

This laboratory modeled Free Space Path Loss (FSPL) using Python. The project analyzed how signal attenuation increases with distance and visualized the results using graphs.

## Technologies

- Python
- NumPy
- Matplotlib

## Skills Developed

- RF propagation analysis
- Python programming
- Data visualization

## Learning Outcome

Understanding path loss is important when designing reliable wireless communication systems and planning network coverage.
